      <body>Here is my patch.

`{Date}Time#in_time_zone`, `Time.use_zone` and `Time.zone=` now raise an `ArgumentError` on invalid timezone arguments.

Note that I changed `test_time_zone_setter_with_invalid_zone` which used to imply that `Time.zone = &quot;foo&quot;` was a no-op. There was no test for `in_time_zone` nor for `use_zone`.

Thanks</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here is my patch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;{Date}Time#in_time_zone&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;Time.use_zone&lt;/code&gt;
and &lt;code&gt;Time.zone=&lt;/code&gt; now raise an &lt;code&gt;ArgumentError&lt;/code&gt;
on invalid timezone arguments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that I changed
&lt;code&gt;test_time_zone_setter_with_invalid_zone&lt;/code&gt; which used to
imply that &lt;code&gt;Time.zone = &quot;foo&quot;&lt;/code&gt; was a no-op. There was no
test for &lt;code&gt;in_time_zone&lt;/code&gt; nor for
&lt;code&gt;use_zone&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
